  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0bb5\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 - \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "We have nothing to do with the Parliament Campus Demonstration - Empty Face Demonstrators",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The empty-faced protestors have declared that they have no connection with the parties who violently protested in the Parliament premises and the Speaker's residence in Uddyogapur. They also requested that the empty-faced protestors' aim was not to capture the buildings, so they should be allowed to take constitutional action.",
        "In this regard, Anurudtha Bandara, one of the main organizers of the empty face protest, said the above in a video posted on his Facebook page.",
        "There have been reports that some parties have gone to the Parliament premises and the Speaker's official residence premises. At the same time that many people visit Khali Mukhatidal, others use them for other activities.",
        "So far, the Presidential Palace, the Presidential Secretariat, the Alari Palace and the Prime Minister's Office have been occupied by protesters or the general public.",
        "The right to engage in peaceful demonstrations is guaranteed. But forced entry into buildings or private establishments can be observed. We request everyone to refrain from such activities.",
        "We should think more intellectually and act with planning than such people. If not, we will get caught up in their activities. The Sri Lanka Bar Association has also requested to stop such activities. So if you engage in the above activities, you will lose their support.",
        "Therefore, the aim of the official group of empty-faced demonstrators is to have the speaker as acting president for a short period of 6 days as per the constitution after the resignation of the president. In this case, it would be an irresponsible action to besiege the house of the Speaker.",
        "Also, it is unfair to pressure the Speaker to keep the President from resigning. Therefore, we request again and again that no one should question their safety by joining the violent gangs."
      ],
